Dear Hiring Team,

It is with great interest that I submit my candidacy for the *Backend Engineer* role with *Standard Metrics*. I bring more than three years of experience building production backend systems and *web applications* in *Python*, *FastAPI*, *PostgreSQL*, *Redis*, *AWS*, *Docker*, and *Kubernetes*, along with a Master of Science in Computer Science from Pace University.

