Standard Metrics' mission to accelerate innovation in the private markets is compelling to me because the product sits at the intersection of durable infrastructure and better decision-making. I especially value your bias toward action in *Take the Next Step* and your commitment to lasting systems in *Build Good Bones* and *Work in the Open*. I would welcome the chance to contribute meaningfully to the team's core engineering responsibilities and help strengthen the automated reporting and benchmarking workflows that investors and portfolio companies rely on every day.

I would love to discuss my fit for this role with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

